sis due to spironolactone." Postgrad Med J 56 (1980):  254-5|Brest AN "Spironolactone in the treatment of hypertension: a review." Clin Ther 8 (1986):  568-85|Jeunemaitre X, Dreft-Jais C, Chatellier G, Julien J, Degoulet P, Plouin P, Menard J, Corvol P "Long-term experience of spironolactone in essential hypertension." Kidney Int 34 Suppl (1988):  s14-7|"Product Information. Midamor (amiloride)." Merck & Co., Inc  (2001):|"Product Information. Aldactone (spironolactone)." Searle  (2001):|Hirschl MM, Seidler D, Laggner AN "Spironolactone-associated hyponatremic coma." Nephron 67 (1994):  503', 'DDInter', 0);
